    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .a {font-size: 12pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 60px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Ш<span class=\"leading\"></span>А Р Т Н О М А</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\">(тўлиқ моддий жавобгарлик тўғрисида)<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"\">{#2}Шартнома тузилган сана</span> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span> <span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"\">{#4}Шартнома рақами</span>-сон <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"\">{#3}Шартнома тузилган жой</span> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#7}Низом</span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Устав </span> асосида фаолият кўрсатувчи, <span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"\">{#9}Иш берувчи ташкилотнинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span> кейинги ўринларда «Иш берувчи» деб юритиладиган <span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"\">{#10} Раҳбарнинг лавозими</span> <span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"\">{#11}Раҳбарнинг Ф.И.О.</span> орқали бир томондан ва кейинги ўринларда «Ходим» деб юритиладиган мазкур ташкилот раҳбарининг <span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"\">{#14}Ходим ишга қабул қилинган сана</span> йилдаги <span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"\">{#15}Ходим ишга қабул қилинган буйруқ рақами</span> сонли буйруғига асосан <span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"\">{#16}Ходимнинг лавозими</span> лавозимида ишлаб келувчи <span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"\">{#13}Ходимнинг Ф.И.О.</span> иккинчи томондан ушбу шартномани қуйидагилар тўғрисида тузишди:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36px; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\">1. “Ходим” моддий жавобгар шахс ҳисобланиб, “Иш берувчи” томонидан ўзига топширилган моддий бойликлар учун тўлиқ жавобгарликни ўз зиммасига олади.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36px; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\">Ҳодимнинг моддий жавобгарлигига <span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"\">{#18}Ходимнинг моддий жавобгарлигига топширилган товар-моддий бойликлар </span>лар топширилади.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36px; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\">2. <span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"\">{#9}Иш берувчи ташкилотнинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span> ходимга ишлаш учун ҳужжатларни, моддий бойлик жиҳозларини сақлаш, уларни топшириш ва қабул қилиб олиш учун талабларга жавоб берадиган бино, иншоот ва хоналар ажратишни ўз зиммасига олади.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36px; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\">3. “Ходим” жамият бўйича чиқариладиган буйруқлар ва фармойишларнинг қатъийян бажарилишини, топширилган моддий бойликларнинг тўлиқлигини, сақлашни, уларнинг ҳисоб-китобларини тўғри олиб боришни ўз зиммасига олади.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36px; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\">4. “Ходим”нинг совуққонлиги ва масъулиятсизлиги туфайли топширилган моддий бойликлардан камомад ёки етишмовчилик чиқиш ҳолатлари аниқланганда Ўзбекистон Республикасининг Меҳнат кодексининг 340-343-моддаларига асосан жамиятга етказилган зарарни тўлиқ тўлашни ўз зиммасига олади.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36px; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\">5. Мазкур шартнома имзоланган кундан кучга киради ва ходим мазкур лавозимда ишлаб турган бутун даврда амал қилади.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36px; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\">Шартнома икки нусхада тузилиб томонларда бир нусхадан сақланади.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 234.6px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">И<span class=\"leading\"></span>М З О Л А Р:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"\">{#9}Иш берувчи ташкилотнинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"\">{#10}Раҳбарнинг лавозими</span> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"\">{#11}Раҳбарнинг Ф.И.О.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\">Шартнома билан танишдим ва бир нусхасини олдим.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"\">{#9}Иш берувчи ташкилотнинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 11.6666666725px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Ходимнинг лавозими</span> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"